{Speech 19 Answer 18}{}{To the worldmap}
{Speech 20}{}{In the center of town, next to an old little church packed with parishioners, stands a Vertibird!@@Aside from the Vertibird there's nothing interesting here. Imagine that, you thought, nobody's swiped it yet!@@A huge winged thing caught your attention. It's some kind of descendant of a helicopter, it seems.}
